`8Keywords``   : Vampiric
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

Weapons with the vampiric flag will cause some hits to steal a small amount of
hp from the target, and add it to your current amount. Each time this occurs,
your alignment will decrease by 1, a gradual shift towards evil.

